OL,6,FMr Kirby's funeral will be held at St
OL,7,FMary Redcliffe in Bristol on Wednesday
OL,8,F15 May.
OL,10,FAhead of the service, his mother
OL,11,FJacqui Kirby said: "As we gather for
OL,12,Fthe funeral service at St Mary's
OL,13,FRedcliffe, to celebrate the life of my
OL,14,Fson, James, I cannot express more
OL,15,Fdeeply my gratitude for the outpouring
OL,16,Fof love I have seen over the weeks
OL,17,Fsince his tragic death in Gaza.
OL,19,F"James was a remarkable man, a true
OL,20,Ffriend to so many people and, above
OL,21,Fall, he was my son.
