OL,6,F"I will miss him beyond measure and
OL,7,Fcannot comprehend a future without his
OL,8,Fpresence.
OL,10,F"But, I take great comfort from
OL,11,Fknowing he died doing something that
OL,12,Freally mattered to him, and the
OL,13,Fknowledge that he was loved by so many
OL,14,Fpeople from all walks of life."
OL,16,FLabour MP Kerry McCarthy told the
OL,17,FCommons last month that Ms Kirby is
OL,18,Fone of her Bristol East constituents.
