OL,6,FShe said to Foreign Office minister
OL,7,FDavid Rutley: "The family want answers
OL,8,Fand I'd really appreciate it if the
OL,9,Fminister could tell the Foreign
OL,10,FSecretary while he's in the region,
OL,11,Fpass that message on from the family `
OL,12,Fthey want answers."
OL,14,FBritons John Chapman, 57, and James
OL,15,F"Jim" Henderson, 33, were also killed
OL,16,Fin the attack and all three British
OL,17,Fcitizens have been repatriated.
