OL,6,FAlso killed were the relief team's
OL,7,Fleader, Australian national Lalzawmi
OL,8,F"Zomi" Frankcom, 43; dual American-
OL,9,FCanadian citizen Jacob Flickinger, 33;
OL,10,FPolish national Damian Sobol, 35; and
OL,11,Ftheir driver, Palestinian Saifeddin
OL,12,FIssam Ayad Abutaha, 25.
OL,14,FA memorial for the relief team was
OL,15,Fheld at the National Cathedral in
OL,16,FWashington DC at the end of April.
