OL,6,FLondon and other Western capitals
OL,7,Fcondemned the strike with Prime
OL,8,FMinister Rishi Sunak telling his
OL,9,FIsraeli counterpart Benjamin Netanyahu
OL,10,Fthat he was "appalled" and that the
OL,11,Fsituation in Gaza is "increasingly
OL,12,Fintolerable".
OL,14,FIt prompted US President Joe Biden's
OL,15,Fadministration to signal for the first
OL,16,Ftime that it might cut military aid to
OL,17,FIsrael if it did not change its
OL,18,Fhandling of the war and humanitarian
OL,19,Faid.
