OL,6,FLast week the administration said
OL,7,FIsrael's use of US-provided weapons in
OL,8,FGaza likely violated international
OL,9,Fhumanitarian law but that it could not
OL,10,Flink specific US weapons to individual
OL,11,Fattacks.
OL,13,FThe Israel Defence Forces (IDF)
OL,14,Fdismissed two officers and reprimanded
OL,15,Fthree others over the incident,
OL,16,Fcalling it a "serious mistake".
